		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item, Legendary</em></p><p>This item first appears to be a sealed iron barrel weighing 500 pounds. The barrel has a hidden catch, which can be found with a successful [[/check ability=int skill=inv dc=20]] check. Releasing the catch unlocks a hatch at one end of the barrel, allowing two Medium or smaller creatures to crawl inside. Ten levers are set in a row at the far end, each in a neutral position, able to move up or down. When certain levers are used, the apparatus transforms to resemble a giant lobster.</p><p>The @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.actors24.Actor.dmgApparatusofKw]{Apparatus of the Crab} is a Large object with the following statistics: AC 20; HP 200; Speed 30 ft., Swim 30 ft. (or 0 ft. for both if the legs aren't extended); Immunity to Poison and Psychic damage.</p><p>@Embed[Compendium.dnd5e.actors24.Actor.dmgApparatusofKw caption=false]</p>",
